HEADWORD: Incorrectness
<hw>In`cor*rect"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
incorrect; lack of conformity to truth or to a standard; inaccuracy;
inexactness; <as>as, <ex>incorrectness</ex> may consist in defect or in
redundance</as>.</def></p>

